{
  "_meta": {
    "purpose": "Output-parity conformance tier (rac-core ADR-063 Guard 2): each case pins the byte-for-byte stdout and exit code an engine must produce for a deterministic, recency-free command run from this repository's root over an example corpus. An engine conforms to this tier when it reproduces every case exactly.",
    "environment": {
      "RAC_NO_CACHE": "1",
      "LC_ALL": "C",
      "TZ": "UTC",
      "COLUMNS": "80"
    },
    "cwd": "the rac-spec repository root",
    "arbiter": "The golden stdout bytes are the reference implementation's (rac-core) exact output. Where this tier and an implementation disagree, rac-core is the arbiter; where this tier and rac-core disagree, that is a spec defect — file an issue."
  },
